libfn provides CMake targets:

    find_package(libfn CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE libfn::pfn)  # C++20-compatible polyfills
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE libfn::fn)   # C++23 required (default)

To disable C++23 features and expose only C++20 compatible components, install with:
    vcpkg install "libfn[disable-cxx23]"
